Package: pharmsolr
Title: R Bindings for pharmsol DSL Runtime Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("pharmsol", "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Defines pharmacometric models in pharmsol's recommended DSL,
    compiles them through the runtime API exposed by the 'pharmsol' Rust
    crate, and runs simulations from R. The package builds the Rust bridge at
    install time; once installed, end users compile and simulate DSL models at
    runtime without invoking 'cargo' or 'rustc' on every call.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
